      "passage_text": "Midbrain dopamine neurons in the ventral tegmental area (VTA) encode reward prediction errors (RPE): they fire above baseline when reward exceeds expectation and are suppressed when expected reward is omitted. Single-unit recordings in 18 macaques across 6,000 trials replicated the RPE signal with high fidelity (R\u00b2 = 0.91)."
