      "passage_text": "Single-cell RNA sequencing of post-mortem human cortex (n = 48 donors, 24 Alzheimer's / 24 controls) identified a disease-associated microglia (DAM) subtype upregulating TREM2 and downregulating homeostatic genes. DAM density correlated with amyloid plaque load (Spearman \u03c1 = 0.74)."
